export const LoginFormLayouts= [
    {
        align: 'left',
        bind: 'textBoxValue',                    
        label: 'User Name: ',
        labelPosition: 'left',
        labelWidth: '30%',
        required: true,
        type: 'text',
        width: '250px'                   
    },
    {
        align: 'left',
        bind: 'passwordBoxValue',                    
        label: 'Password: ',
        labelPosition: 'left',
        labelWidth: '30%',
        required: true,
        type: 'password',
        width: '250px'                    
    },
    {
        align: 'left',
        bind: 'checkboxValue2',
        width: "100%",
        columnWidth: '100%',                                
        text: 'Login/SignIn',                                
        labelPadding: { left: 0, top: 5, right: 0, bottom: 5 },
        labelPosition: 'left',
        name: "Login",
        type: 'button'
    },
    
];
